#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started with Vaadin"
msgstr "开始使用 Vaadin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter gives practical instructions for installing the recommended "
"toolchain, the Vaadin libraries and its dependencies, and creating a new "
"Vaadin project."
msgstr ""
"本章介绍如何安装 Vaadin 推荐的开发工具群、Vaadin 库以及它依赖的其他库, 以及如"
"何创建新的 Vaadin 工程."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can develop Vaadin applications in essentially any development "
"environment that has the Java SDK and a Java Servlet container. Vaadin has "
"special support for the Eclipse IDE, but community support exists also for "
"the NetBeans IDE and IntelliJ IDEA, and you can use it with any Java IDE or "
"no IDE at all."
msgstr ""
"本质上说, 只要带有 Java SDK 和 Java Servlet 容器, 你可以使用任何开发环境来开"
"发 Vaadin 应用程序. Vaadin 对 Eclipse IDE 有特别的支持, 但对于 NetBeans IDE "
"和 IntelliJ IDEA, 也有开发者社区提供支持, 你也可以使用其他任何 Java IDE , 甚"
"至完全不使用 IDE ."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Managing Vaadin and other Java libraries can get tedious to do manually, so "
"using a build system that manages dependencies automatically is adviced. "
"Vaadin is distributed in the Maven central repository, and can be used with "
"any build or dependency management system that can access Maven repository, "
"such as Ivy or Gradle, in addition to Maven."
msgstr ""
"手动管理 Vaadin 库及其他 Java 库将会是十分枯燥无聊的, 因此我们建议使用某种能"
"够自动管理包依赖关系的 build 工具. Vaadin 通过 Maven central repository 发"
"布, 因此任何一种能够访问 Maven  库的 build 工具或包依赖管理工具都可以使用 "
"Vaadin, 比如 Ivy, Gradle, 或 Maven."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vaadin has a multitude of installation options for different IDEs, "
"dependency managers, and you can also install it from an installation "
"package:"
msgstr ""
"对于不同的 IDE, 包依赖管理工具, Vaadin 有多种不同的安装方法, 另外你也可以使用"
"安装包来安装 Vaadin:"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the Eclipse IDE, use the Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse, as described in "
"<xref linkend=\"getting-started.eclipse\"/>"
msgstr ""
"对于 Eclipse IDE, 请使用 Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse, 详情参见 <xref linkend="
"\"getting-started.eclipse\"/>"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the Vaadin plugin for NetBeans IDE (<xref linkend=\"getting-started."
"netbeans\"/>) or IntelliJ IDEA"
msgstr ""
"使用 Vaadin plugin for NetBeans IDE (<xref linkend=\"getting-started.netbeans"
"\"/>) 或 IntelliJ IDEA"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With Maven, Ivy, Gradle, or other Maven-compatible dependency manager, under "
"Eclipse, NetBeans, IDEA, or using command-line, as described in <xref "
"linkend=\"getting-started.maven\"/>"
msgstr ""
"使用 Maven, Ivy, Gradle, 或其他的 Maven兼容的包依赖管理工具, 可用于 Eclipse, "
"NetBeans, IDEA, 或使用命令行工具, 详情参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-started."
"maven\"/>"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From installation package without dependency management, as described in "
"<xref linkend=\"getting-started.package\"/>"
msgstr ""
"无包依赖管理工具时, 请使用安装包, 详情参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-started."
"package\"/>"

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting up the Development Environment"
msgstr "设置开发环境"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section guides you step-by-step in setting up a reference development "
"environment. Vaadin supports a wide variety of tools, so you can use any IDE "
"for writing the code, almost any Java web server for deploying the "
"application, most web browsers for using it, and any operating system "
"platform supported by Java."
msgstr ""
"本节指导你设置一个参考性的开发环境. Vaadin 支持非常多的开发工具, 因此你可以使"
"用任何 IDE 编写代码, 可以使用几乎任何一种 Java web 服务器来发布应用程序, 可以"
"用任何大多数 Web 浏览器来使用你的应用程序, 可以使用Java 支持的任何一种操作系"
"统"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this example, we use the following toolchain:"
msgstr "在本节的示例中, 我们使用以下工具群:"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windows, Linux, or Mac OS X"
msgstr "Windows, Linux, 或 Mac OS X"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp\">Sun Java "
"2 Standard Edition 6.0</link> (JDK 1.6 or newer is required)"
msgstr ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp\">Sun Java "
"2 Standard Edition 6.0</link> (需要 JDK 1.6 或更高版本)"

#. Tag: link
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: link
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apache Tomcat 7.0 (Core) or newer"
msgstr "Apache Tomcat 7.0 (Core) 或更高版本"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://www.getfirefox.com/\">Mozilla Firefox</link> "
"browser"
msgstr ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://www.getfirefox.com/\">Mozilla Firefox</link> 浏览器"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://www.getfirebug.com/\">Firebug</link> debug tool "
"(optional)"
msgstr ""
"<link xlink:href=\"http://www.getfirebug.com/\">Firebug</link> 调试工具 (可"
"选)"

#. Tag: link
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vaadin Framework"
msgstr "Vaadin 框架"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above reference toolchain is a good choice of tools, but you can use "
"almost any tools you are comfortable with."
msgstr "上述工具群是一组很好的选择, 但你也可以自由选择你所熟悉的其他工具."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We recommend using Java 8 for Vaadin development, but you need to make sure "
"that your entire toolchain supports it. If you intend to use server push, "
"you need to use at least Java EE 7 compatible server with WebSocket support, "
"such as Glassfish, TomEE, etc."
msgstr ""
"开发 Vaadin 应用程序时, 我们建议使用 Java 8, 但你需要确认你的整个开发环境是否"
"全部支持 Java 8. 如果你打算使用服务器端 PUSH 功能 , 你需要使用至少兼容 Java "
"EE 7, 并支持 WebSocket 功能的服务器, 比如 Glassfish, TomEE, 等等."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Development Toolchain and Process"
msgstr "开发用工具群以及开发流程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"illustrates the development toolchain. You develop your application as an "
"Eclipse project. The project must include, in addition to your source code, "
"the Vaadin libraries. It can also include project-specific themes."
msgstr ""
"描述了开发中使用到的工具群. 应用程序以 Eclipse 过程的形式编写. 除你的应用程序"
"源代码之外, 工程还必须包括 Vaadin 库. 也可以包含工程独有的 theme."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to compile and deploy a project to a web container before you can "
"use it. You can deploy a project through the Web Tools Platform (WTP) for "
"Eclipse (included in the Eclipse EE package), which allows automatic "
"deployment of web applications from Eclipse. You can also deploy a project "
"manually, by creating a web application archive (WAR) and deploying it to "
"the web container."
msgstr ""
"你需要编译你的工程, 并发布到 Web 容器中, 之后你才能使用你的应用程序. 在 "
"Eclipse 环境中, 工程的发布可以使用 WTP (Web Tools Platform)(已包含在 Eclipse "
"EE 包中), WTP 可以从 Eclipse 环境中自动发布 Web 应用程序. 你也可以手动发布工"
"程, 方法是创建一个WAR ( Web application archive), 然后将它发布到 Web 容器中."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Java SDK"
msgstr "安装 Java SDK"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Java SDK is required by Vaadin and also by the Eclipse IDE. Vaadin is "
"compatible with Java 1.6 and later editions. Java EE 7 is required for "
"proper server push support with WebSockets."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 和 Eclipse IDE 都需要依赖于 Java SDK. (译注: 此处不正确, Eclipse IDE "
"自带编译器, 因此它只需要 JRE, 不一定需要 JDK. Vaadin 不明) Vaadin 兼容于 "
"Java 1.6 及以后版本. 如果通过 WebSocket 实现服务器端 PUSH 功能, 则需要 Java "
"EE 7."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:132 chapter-getting-started.xml:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windows"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download Sun Java 2 Standard Edition 7.0 from <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html\"> http://www.oracle."
"com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html</link>"
msgstr ""
"下载 Sun Java 2 Standard Edition 7.0, 地址是 <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html\"> http://www.oracle."
"com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Install the Java SDK by running the installer. The default options are fine."
msgstr "运行安装程序即可安装 Java SDK. 安装过程中使用默认选项即可."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Linux / UNIX"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most Linux systems either have JDK preinstalled or allow installing it "
"through a package management system. Notice however that they have OpenJDK "
"as the default Java implementation. While it is known to have worked with "
"Vaadin and possibly also with the development toolchain, we do not "
"especially support it."
msgstr ""
"大多数 Linux 系统要么已预装有 JDK, 要么允许你通过包管理系统安装 JDK. 但请注"
"意, Linux 系统一般都选用 OpenJDK 作为默认的 Java 实现. 尽管 OpenJDK 已被测试"
"过可以支持 Vaadin, 而且也可能支持开发用的工具群, 但我们并不对 OpenJDK 提供特"
"别的支持."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Regarding OS X, notice that JDK 1.6 or newer is included in OS X 10.6 and "
"newer."
msgstr ""
"对于 OS X 系统, 请注意在 OS X 10.6 或以上版本已包含了 JDK 1.6 或以上版本."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Otherwise:"
msgstr "其他情况:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download Sun Java 2 Standard Edition 6.0 from <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html\"> http://www.oracle."
"com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/</link>"
msgstr ""
"下载 Sun Java 2 Standard Edition 6.0 , 地址是 <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html\"> http://www.oracle."
"com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decompress it under a suitable base directory, such as <filename>/opt</"
"filename>. For example, for Java SDK, enter (either as root or with "
"<command>sudo</command> in Linux): <screen><prompt>#</prompt> <command>cd</"
"command> <replaceable>/opt</replaceable>\n"
"<prompt>#</prompt> <command>sh</command> <replaceable>(path-to-installation-"
"package)/jdk-7u1-linux-i586.bin</replaceable></screen> and follow the "
"instructions in the installer."
msgstr ""
"在某个适当的目录, 例如 <filename>/opt</filename>, 将下载的安装包解压. 例如, "
"对于 Java SDK, 输入以下命令 (在 Linux 下需要以 root 帐号运行, 或通过 "
"<command>sudo</command> 运行): <screen><prompt>#</prompt> <command>cd</"
"command> <replaceable>/opt</replaceable>\n"
"<prompt>#</prompt> <command>sh</command> <replaceable>(path-to-installation-"
"package)/jdk-7u1-linux-i586.bin</replaceable></screen> 然后遵照安装程序的指示"
"进行."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set up the <literal>JAVA_HOME</literal> environment variable to point to the "
"Java installation directory. Also, include the <literal>$JAVA_HOME/bin</"
"literal> in the <literal>PATH</literal>. How you do that varies by the UNIX "
"variant. For example, in Linux and using the Bash shell, you would add lines "
"such as the following to the <filename>.bashrc</filename> or <filename>."
"profile</filename> script in your home directory: <screen>export JAVA_HOME=/"
"opt/jdk1.7.0_01\n"
"export PATH=$PATH:$HOME/bin:$JAVA_HOME/bin</screen> You could also make the "
"setting system-wide in a file such as <filename>/etc/bash.bashrc</filename>, "
"<filename>/etc/profile</filename>, or an equivalent file. If you install "
"Apache Ant or Maven, you may also want to set up those in the path."
msgstr ""
"设置 <literal>JAVA_HOME</literal> 环境变量, 指向到 Java 安装目录. 另外, 还需"
"要将 <literal>$JAVA_HOME/bin</literal> 目录追加到 <literal>PATH</literal> 环"
"境变量中. 具体方法根据你使用的 UNIX 版本不同而不同. 比如, 在 Linux 中使用 "
"Bash shell 时, 你需要将以下内容添加到你的 home 目录下的 <filename>.bashrc</"
"filename> 或 <filename>.profile</filename> 文件中: <screen>export JAVA_HOME=/"
"opt/jdk1.7.0_01\n"
"export PATH=$PATH:$HOME/bin:$JAVA_HOME/bin</screen> 你也可以将上述设定设置为"
"全系统所有用户的公共设定, 方法是将上述内容添加到 <filename>/etc/bash.bashrc</"
"filename>, 或 <filename>/etc/profile</filename>, 或者你的 Linux 系统的某个等"
"价的文件中. 如果你安装了 Apache Ant 或 Maven, 你也许希望将它们也添加到 path "
"路径中."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings done in a <filename>bashrc</filename> file require that you open a "
"new shell window. Settings done in a <filename>profile</filename> file "
"require that you log in into the system. You can, of course, also give the "
"commands in the current shell."
msgstr ""
"如果通过 <filename>bashrc</filename> 文件进行设定, 那么你需要打开一个新的 "
"shell 窗口才能让这些设定生效. 如果通过 <filename>profile</filename>  文件进行"
"设定, 则需要你退出系统并重新 login 一次才能让这些设定生效. 当然, 你也可以在当"
"前的shell 中执行上述设定命令, 设定将立即生效."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Eclipse IDE"
msgstr "安装 Eclipse IDE"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download the Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers from <link xlink:href="
"\"http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/\"> http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/</"
"link>"
msgstr ""
"下载 Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers , 地址是 <link xlink:href=\"http://"
"www.eclipse.org/downloads/\"> http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decompress the Eclipse IDE package to a suitable directory. You are free to "
"select any directory and to use any ZIP decompressor, but in this example we "
"decompress the ZIP file by just double-clicking it and selecting \"Extract "
"all files\" task from Windows compressed folder task. In our installation "
"example, we use <filename>C:\\dev</filename> as the target directory."
msgstr ""
"在某个适当的目录解压 Eclipse IDE 安装包. 你完全可以选择你喜欢的任何一个 ZIP "
"解压程序, 你可以把文件解压到你喜欢的任何目录, 但在本示例中, 我们双击 ZIP 文"
"件, 然后在 Windows 的压缩目录中选择 \"解压缩有文件\". 在我们的示例中, 我们使"
"用 <filename>C:\\dev</filename> 作为解压目录."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eclipse is now installed in <filename>C:\\dev\\eclipse</filename> and can be "
"started from there (by double clicking eclipse.exe)."
msgstr ""
"执行以上操作之后, Eclipse 将被安装到 <filename>C:\\dev\\eclipse</filename> , "
"在这个目录下双击 eclipse.exe 即可启动 Eclipse."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Linux / OS X / UNIX"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We recommend that you install Eclipse manually in Linux and other UNIX "
"variants as follows."
msgstr "在 Linux 或其他 UNIX 系统下, 我们建议手动安装 Eclipse, 方法如下."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers from <link xlink:href=\"http://"
"www.eclipse.org/downloads/\"> http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/</link>"
msgstr ""
"下载 Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers, 地址是 <link xlink:href=\"http://"
"www.eclipse.org/downloads/\"> http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decompress the Eclipse package into a suitable base directory. It is "
"important to make sure that there is no old Eclipse installation in the "
"target directory. Installing a new version on top of an old one probably "
"renders Eclipse unusable."
msgstr ""
"在适当的目录下解压 Eclipse 包. 注意, 目标目录下一定不要有旧的 Eclipse 存在. "
"在既有的 Eclipse 目录中安装新版本的 Eclipse 可能会造成它无法运行."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eclipse should normally be installed as a regular user, as this makes "
"installation of plugins easier. Eclipse also stores some user settings in "
"the installation directory. To install the package, enter: <screen><prompt>"
"$</prompt> <command>tar</command> zxf <replaceable>(path-to-installation-"
"package)/eclipse-jee-ganymede-SR2-linux-gtk.tar.gz</replaceable></screen> "
"This will extract the package to a subdirectory with the name "
"<filename>eclipse</filename>."
msgstr ""
"一般来说应该以一般用户身份来安装 Eclipse, 这样的话将来安装插件会容易一些. "
"Eclipse 也会在它的安装目录下保存一些用户设置信息. 安装 Eclipse 请执行以下命"
"令: <screen><prompt>$</prompt> <command>tar</command> zxf <replaceable>(path-"
"to-installation-package)/eclipse-jee-ganymede-SR2-linux-gtk.tar.gz</"
"replaceable></screen> 以上命令会将安装包解压到一个名为 <filename>eclipse</"
"filename> 的子目录中."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to enable starting Eclipse from command-line, you need to add "
"the Eclipse installation directory to your system or user PATH, or make a "
"symbolic link or script to point to the executable."
msgstr ""
"如果你希望能够从命令行启动 Eclipse, 你需要将 Eclipse 安装目录追加到你的系统 "
"PATH 路径或当前用户 PATH 路径中去, 也可以创建一个符号链接, 或创建一个脚本, 指"
"向 Eclipse 的可执行程序."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alternative to the above procedure would be to use an Eclipse version "
"available through the package management system of your operating system. It "
"is, however, <emphasis>not recommended</emphasis>, because you will need "
"write access to the Eclipse installation directory to install Eclipse "
"plugins, and you may face incompatibility issues with Eclipse plugins "
"installed by the package management of the operating system."
msgstr ""
"除了以上手动安装方法之外, 另一种替代方法是通过你的操作系统的包管理工具来安装 "
"Eclipse. 但是,我们<emphasis>不推荐</emphasis>这种方法, 因为当你安装 Eclipse "
"插件时, 你将需要对 Eclipse 安装目录的写权限, 而且, 由操作系统的包管理工具安装"
"的 Eclipse 可能并非最新版本, 因此导致版本兼容问题."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Apache Tomcat"
msgstr "安装 Apache Tomcat"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apache Tomcat is a lightweight Java web server suitable for both development "
"and production. There are many ways to install it, but here we simply "
"decompress the installation package."
msgstr ""
"Apache Tomcat 是一种轻量级 Java Web 服务器, 既可用于开发环境, 也可用于生产环"
"境. 安装 Apache Tomcat 的方法很多, 在本示例中我们只简单的解压 Apache Tomcat "
"的安装包."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Apache Tomcat should be installed with user permissions.</"
"emphasis> During development, you will be running Eclipse or some other IDE "
"with user permissions, but deploying web applications to a Tomcat server "
"that is installed system-wide requires administrator or root permissions."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>应该使用一般用户权限来安装 Apache Tomcat.</emphasis> 开发阶段中, 你"
"通常会用一般用户权限来运行 Eclipse 或其他 IDE, 如果 Tomcat 服务器不是某个用户"
"专有而是系统级服务, 那么向 Tomcat 服务器发布 Web 应用程序将需要管理员或 root "
"权限."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download the installation package:"
msgstr "下载安装包:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apache Tomcat 7.0 (Core Binary Distribution) from <uri>http://tomcat.apache."
"org/</uri>"
msgstr ""
"下载 Apache Tomcat 7.0 (Core Binary Distribution), 地址是 <uri>http://tomcat."
"apache.org/</uri>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decompress Apache Tomcat package to a suitable target directory, such as "
"<filename>C:\\dev</filename> (Windows) or <filename>/opt</filename> (Linux "
"or Mac OS X). The Apache Tomcat home directory will be <filename>C:\\dev"
"\\apache-tomcat-7.0.x</filename> or <filename>/opt/apache-tomcat-7.0.x</"
"filename>, respectively."
msgstr ""
"在某个适当的目录解压 Apache Tomcat 包, 比如 <filename>C:\\dev</filename> "
"(Windows 系统) 或 <filename>/opt</filename> (Linux 或 Mac OS X 系统). Apache "
"Tomcat 的主目录将是 <filename>C:\\dev\\apache-tomcat-7.0.x</filename> 或 "
"<filename>/opt/apache-tomcat-7.0.x</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Firefox and Firebug"
msgstr "Firefox 和 Firebug"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vaadin supports many web browsers and you can use any of them for "
"development. If you plan to create a custom theme, customized layouts, or "
"create new components, we recommend that you use either Firefox together "
"with Firebug or Google Chrome, which has built-in developer tools similar to "
"Firebug."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 支持很多种 Web 浏览器, 你可以使用其中任何一种用于开发. 如果你打算创建"
"自定义的theme, 定制化的布局, 或者创建新组件, 我们建议你使用 Firefox 浏览器配"
"合调试工具 Firebug , 或者使用 Google Chrome 浏览器, 其中带有内建的调试工具, "
"与 Firebug 类似."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Firebug with Vaadin"
msgstr "使用 Firebug 调试 Vaadin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After installing Firefox, use it to open <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"getfirebug.com/\"> http://www.getfirebug.com/</link>. Follow the "
"instructions on the site to install the latest stable version of Firebug "
"available for the browser. You may need to allow Firefox to install the "
"plugin by clicking the yellow warning bar at the top of the browser window."
msgstr ""
"安装完 Firefox 后, 使用它打开以下地址: <link xlink:href=\"http://www."
"getfirebug.com/\"> http://www.getfirebug.com/</link>. 遵照网站上的指示即可安"
"装最新版本的 Firebug. 要允许 Firefox 安装插件, 你可能需要点击浏览器窗口顶端的"
"黄色警告条."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After Firebug is installed, it can be enabled at any time from the Firefox "
"toolbar. <xref linkend=\"figure.firebug.calc\"/> shows Firebug in action."
msgstr ""
"Firebug 安装完成后, 你随时可以通过 Firefox 工具条激活它. <xref linkend="
"\"figure.firebug.calc\"/> 展示了 Firebug 激活后的状况."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Firebug Debugger for Firefox"
msgstr "Firefox 调试工具 Firebug"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important feature in Firebug is inspecting HTML elements. Right-"
"click on an element and select <guilabel>Inspect Element with Firebug</"
"guilabel> to inspect it. In addition to HTML tree, it also shows the CSS "
"rules matching the element, which you can use for building themes. You can "
"even edit the CSS styles live, to experiment with styling."
msgstr ""
"Firebug 最重要的功能是查看页面中的 HTML 元素. 在某个页面元素上点击鼠标右键, "
"然后在菜单中选择<guilabel>Inspect Element with Firebug</guilabel> 即可查看这"
"个元素. Firebug 将显示 HTML 元素的树型构造, 除此之外还显示适用到各个元素上的 "
"CSS 规则, 我们构建 theme 时使用的正是这些 CSS 规则. 你也可以在运行中修改 CSS "
"风格的内容, 随时验证各种风格的实际效果."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of Vaadin Libraries"
msgstr "Vaadin 库概述"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vaadin comes as a set of library JARs, of which some are optional or "
"alternative ones, depending on whether you are developing server-side or "
"client-side applications, whether you use add-on components, or use CSS or "
"Sass themes."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 带有很多 JAR 库文件, 有些库文件是可选的, 有些是可以相互替代的, 具体情"
"况取决于你开发的是服务器端还是客户端应用程序, 取决于你是否使用了 add-on 组"
"件, 也取决于你使用 CSS 还是 Sass 的 theme."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-server-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main library for developing server-side Vaadin applications, as "
"described in <xref linkend=\"application\"/>. It requires the "
"<filename>vaadin-shared</filename> and the <filename>vaadin-themes</"
"filename> libraries. You can use the prebuilt <filename>vaadin-client-"
"compiled</filename> for server-side development, unless you need add-on "
"components or custom widgets."
msgstr ""
"这是用于开发服务器端 Vaadin 应用程序的主要库文件, 详情见 <xref linkend="
"\"application\"/>. 这个库文件依赖于 <filename>vaadin-shared</filename> 和 "
"<filename>vaadin-themes</filename> 库文件. 如果你没有用到 add-on 组件和定制"
"化 widget 的话, 一般来说你可以使用预编译的 <filename>vaadin-client-compiled</"
"filename> 进行服务器端开发."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-shared-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A shared library for server-side and client-side development. It is always "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"服务器端开发与客户端开发使用到的共通库文件. 一般来说这个库文件总是需要的."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-client-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The client-side Vaadin framework, including the basic GWT API and Vaadin-"
"specific widgets and other additions. It is required when using the "
"<filename>vaadin-client-compiler</filename> to compile client-side modules. "
"It is not needed if you just use the server-side framework with the "
"precompiled Client-Side Engine. You should not deploy it with a web "
"application."
msgstr ""
"客户端 Vaadin 框架, 包含基本的 GWT API 和 Vaadin 独有的 widget, 以及其他附加"
"内容. 当使用  <filename>vaadin-client-compiler</filename> 编译客户端模块时, "
"需要用到这个库文件. 如果你的开发中只使用到服务器端框架和预编译的客户端引擎, "
"那么这个库文件就是不必用到的. 这个库文件不应该随 Web 应用程序一起发布到运行环"
"境."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-client-compiler-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vaadin Client Compiler is a Java-to-JavaScript compiler that allows "
"building client-side modules, such as the Client-Side Engine (widget set) "
"required for server-side applications. The compiler is needed, for example, "
"for compiling add-on components to the application widget set, as described "
"in <xref linkend=\"addons\"/>. For detailed information regarding the "
"compiler, see <xref linkend=\"clientside.compiling\"/>. Note that you should "
"not deploy this library with a web application."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 客户端编译器是一个从 Java 到 JavaScript 的编译器, 可用于创建客户端模"
"块, 如服务器应用程序所需要的客户端引擎(widget 群). 编译器的应用场合, 举例来"
"说, 可以将 add-on 组件编译为应用程序的 widget 群, 详情参见 <xref linkend="
"\"addons\"/>. 关于编译器的详细情况, 参见 <xref linkend=\"clientside.compiling"
"\"/>. 注意, 这个库不应该随 Web 应用程序一起发布到运行环境."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-client-compiled-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A precompiled Vaadin Client-Side Engine (widget set) that includes all the "
"basic built-in widgets in Vaadin. This library is not needed if you compile "
"the application widget set with the Vaadin Client Compiler."
msgstr ""
"这个库是预编译的 Vaadin 客户端引擎(widget 群), 包含Vaadin 内建的基本的 "
"widget. 如果你使用 Vaadin 客户端编译器来编译应用程序的 widget 群, 那么这个库"
"是不必用到的."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-themes-&version.vaadin;.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vaadin built-in themes both as SCSS source files and precompiled CSS files. "
"The library is required both for basic use with CSS themes and for compiling "
"custom Sass themes."
msgstr ""
"这个库是 Vaadin 的内建 theme, 包含 SCSS 源文件, 以及预编译的 CSS 文件. 不论是"
"使用基本的 CSS theme , 还是编译 Sass theme, 都需要使用这个库."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "vaadin-sass-compiler-1.x.x.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vaadin Sass Compiler compiles Sass themes to CSS, as described in <xref "
"linkend=\"themes.sass\"/>. It requires the <filename>vaadin-themes-&version."
"vaadin;.jar</filename> library, which contains the Sass sources for the "
"built-in themes. The library needs to be included in deployment in "
"development mode to allow on-the-fly compilation of themes, but it is not "
"needed in production deployment, when the themes are compiled before "
"deployment."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin Sass 编译器负责将 Sass theme 编译为 CSS, 详情请参见 <xref linkend="
"\"themes.sass\"/>. 这个库文件依赖于 <filename>vaadin-themes-&version.vaadin;."
"jar</filename>, 其中包含 Vaadin 内建 theme 的 Sass 源文件. 在开发模式下, 为了"
"能够实时编译 theme, 需要将这个库文件包含在发布内容中, 但在生产环境下, 发布之"
"前会预编译 theme , 因此应用程序发布时不需要包含这个库文件."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the libraries depend on each other as well as on the dependency "
"libraries provided in the <filename>lib</filename> folder of the "
"installation package, especially the <filename>lib/vaadin-shared-deps.jar</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"以上各个库文件, 有些会有相互依赖, 而且它们还依赖于安装包的 <filename>lib</"
"filename> 文件夹内提供的其他库文件, 尤其是 <filename>lib/vaadin-shared-deps."
"jar</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The different ways to install the libraries are described in the subsequent "
"sections."
msgstr "库文件的几种安装方法将在后续章节中详细介绍."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the <filename>vaadin-client-compiler</filename> and "
"<filename>vaadin-client</filename> JARs should not be deployed with the web "
"application by including them in <filename>WEB-INF/lib</filename>. Some "
"other libraries, such as <filename>vaadin-sass-compiler</filename>, are not "
"needed in production deployment."
msgstr ""
"注意, <filename>vaadin-client-compiler</filename> 和 <filename>vaadin-"
"client</filename> 库文件不应该与 Web 应用程序一起发布, 因此不要把它们放在 "
"Web 应用程序的 <filename>WEB-INF/lib</filename> 文件夹下. 其他某些库, 比如 "
"<filename>vaadin-sass-compiler</filename>, 只在开发环境下需要, 在生产环境下发"
"布时也是不需要的."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse"
msgstr "安装 Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using the Eclipse IDE, using the Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse helps "
"greatly. Notice that you can also create Vaadin projects as Maven projects "
"in Eclipse."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用的是 Eclipse IDE, 那么 Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse 将对你的开发提供很"
"大的帮助. 注意, 在 Eclipse 中你也可以用 Maven 工程的方式创建 Vaadin 工程."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "The plugin includes:"
msgstr "本 plugin 包括:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Wizards</emphasis> for creating new Vaadin-based projects, themes, "
"and client-side widgets and widget sets."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>向导</emphasis>, 可用于创建新的 Vaadin 工程, theme, 客户端 widget "
"或 widget 群."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis>visual editor</emphasis> for creating composite user interface "
"components in a WYSIWYG fashion. With full round-trip support from source "
"code to visual model and back, the editor integrates seamlessly with your "
"development process."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>可视化编辑器</emphasis>, 以所见即所得的(WYSIWYG)方式创建组合式 UI "
"组件. 可视化编辑器支持从源代码到可视模型, 以及从可视模型到源代码的双方向转换"
"能力, 因此这个编辑器可以与你的整个开发流程紧密融合在一起."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing the IvyDE Plugin"
msgstr "安装 IvyDE Plugin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse requires the Apache IvyDE plugin, which needs "
"to be installed manually in Eclipse before the Vaadin plugin."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse 依赖于 Apache IvyDE plugin, 因此在安装 Vaadin "
"plugin之前需要手动安装 Apache IvyDE plugin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:571 chapter-getting-started.xml:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Install New "
"Software...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"选择以下菜单项: <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Install New "
"Software...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the IvyDE update site by clicking the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr "按下 <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> 按钮, 添加 IvyDE 的更新站点地址."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a name such as \"Apache Ivy Update Site\" and the URL of the update "
"site: <screen>http://www.apache.org/dist/ant/ivyde/updatesite</screen> Then "
"click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The update site should now appear in the "
"<guilabel>Available Software</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"输入一个名称, 比如 \"Apache Ivy Update Site\", 再输入更新站点 URL: "
"<screen>http://www.apache.org/dist/ant/ivyde/updatesite</screen> 然后点击 "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮. Apache Ivy 的更新站点将出现在"
"<guilabel>Available Software</guilabel> 窗口中."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the new \"Apache Ivy Update Site\" from the <guilabel>Work with</"
"guilabel> list."
msgstr ""
"在<guilabel>Work with</guilabel> 列表中选择我们上面新添加的 \"Apache Ivy "
"Update Site\"."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Apache Ivy</guilabel>, <guilabel>Apache Ivy Ant Tasks</"
"guilabel>, and <guilabel>Apache IvyDE</guilabel> plugins."
msgstr ""
"选择 <guilabel>Apache Ivy</guilabel>, <guilabel>Apache Ivy Ant Tasks</"
"guilabel>, 以及 <guilabel>Apache IvyDE</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Apache IvyDE Resolve Visualizer</guilabel> is optional, and "
"would require additional dependency plugins to be installed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Apache IvyDE Resolve Visualizer</guilabel> 是可选的, 如果选择安装"
"它, 会导致其他一些被依赖的插件也被安装进来."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:615 chapter-getting-started.xml:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Then, click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr "然后, 点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:619 chapter-getting-started.xml:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review the installation details and click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"确认一下即将安装的插件的详细信息, 无问题的话, 点击 <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:623 chapter-getting-started.xml:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Accept or unaccept the license. Finally, click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"选择接受或不接受许可协议. 最后, 点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eclipse may warn about unsigned content. If you feel safe, click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Eclipse 可能会警告说某些内容没有数字签名. 如果你觉得没问题的话, 点击 "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the plugin is installed, Eclipse will ask to restart itself. You can "
"proceed to install the Vaadin plugin before the restart, as described in the "
"following section, so you can answer <guibutton>Apply Changes Now</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"插件安装完成后, Eclipse 将提示需要重新启动. 你可以暂时不必重启, 等待安装完 "
"Vaadin plugin 后再重启, 安装方法见后续章节, 所以这时你可以选择 "
"<guibutton>Apply Changes Now</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing the Vaadin Plugin"
msgstr "安装 Vaadin Plugin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can install the plugin as follows:"
msgstr "本插件的安装方法如下:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the Vaadin plugin update site by clicking <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr "点击 <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> 按钮, 添加 Vaadin plugin 更新站点."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a name such as \"Vaadin Update Site\" and the URL of the update site: "
"<uri>http://vaadin.com/eclipse</uri>. If you want or need to use the latest "
"unstable plugin, which is usually more compatible with development and beta "
"releases of Vaadin, you can use <uri>http://vaadin.com/eclipse/experimental</"
"uri> and give it a distinctive name such as \"Vaadin Experimental Site\". "
"Then click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The Vaadin site should now appear in "
"the <guilabel>Available Software</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"输入一个名称, 如 \"Vaadin Update Site\", 然后输入更新站点 URL: <uri>http://"
"vaadin.com/eclipse</uri>. 本插件的最新的、非稳定版本更适合于 Vaadin 的开发中"
"版本或 beta 发布版, 如果你希望使用, 可以输入以下地址: <uri>http://vaadin.com/"
"eclipse/experimental</uri>, 并为它指定一个单独的名称, 比如 \"Vaadin "
"Experimental Site\". 然后点击 <guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮. Vaadin 更新站点"
"将出现在 <guilabel>Available Software</guilabel> 窗口中."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently, if using the stable plugin, the <guilabel>Group items by "
"category</guilabel> should be enabled. If using the experimental plugin, it "
"should be disabled. This may change in future."
msgstr ""
"目前, 如果使用本插件的稳定版本, <guilabel>Group items by category</guilabel> "
"选项将变为有效. 如果使用本插件的试验版本, 这个选项将变为无效. 但这一点将来可"
"能会有变化."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select all the Vaadin plugins in the tree."
msgstr "在插件树中选择所有的 Vaadin 插件."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the plugin is installed, Eclipse will ask to restart itself. Click "
"<guibutton>Restart</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"插件安装完成后, Eclipse 将提示需要重新启动. 点击 <guibutton>Restart</"
"guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use the visual editor, Eclipse must have the internal browser "
"enabled. Most operating system distributions include a suitable browser "
"engine, but if not, you may need to install one as described in <xref "
"linkend=\"eclipse\"/>."
msgstr ""
"如果你需要使用可视化编辑器, Eclipse 的内嵌浏览器必须设置为有效. 大多数操作系"
"统上的 Eclipse 发行版都包含了一个适当的浏览器引擎, 如果没有, 你可能需要自行安"
"装, 详情请参见 <xref linkend=\"eclipse\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More installation instructions for the Eclipse plugin can be found at <link "
"xlink:href=\"http://vaadin.com/eclipse\">http://vaadin.com/eclipse</link>."
msgstr ""
"关于 Eclipse plugin 安装的更多指导信息, 请参见 <link xlink:href=\"http://"
"vaadin.com/eclipse\">http://vaadin.com/eclipse</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating the Plugins"
msgstr "更新插件"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have automatic updates enabled in Eclipse (see "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preferences</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Install/Update</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Automatic Updates</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>), the Vaadin plugin will be updated automatically "
"along with other plugins. Otherwise, you can update the Vaadin plugin "
"manually as follows:"
msgstr ""
"如果你在 Eclipse 中打开了自动更新选项(参见菜单项 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preferences</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Install/Update</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Automatic Updates</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>), Vaadin plugin 将会与其他插件一样自动更新. 如果没"
"有打开自动更新选项, 你可以手动更新它, 方法如下:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check for Updates</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Eclipse will contact the update sites of the "
"installed software."
msgstr ""
"选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check for "
"Updates</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Eclipse 将访问已安装的各个插件的更新站点."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the updates are installed, Eclipse will ask to restart itself. Click "
"<guibutton>Restart</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"更新安装完成后, Eclipse 将提示需要重新启动. 点击 <guibutton>Restart</"
"guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that updating the Vaadin plugin updates only the plugin and "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> the Vaadin libraries, which are project specific. "
"See below for instructions for updating the libraries."
msgstr ""
"注意更新 Vaadin plugin 时将只更新插件本身, 而<emphasis>不会</emphasis> 更新 "
"Vaadin 库, Vaadin 库的版本是由各工程分别指定的. 更新Vaadin 库的方法请见下一"
"节."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating the Vaadin Libraries"
msgstr "更新 Vaadin 库"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Updating the Vaadin plugin does not update Vaadin libraries. The libraries "
"are project specific, as a different version might be required for different "
"projects, so you have to update them separately for each project."
msgstr ""
"更新 Vaadin plugin 不会更新 Vaadin 库. 库的版本是由各工程分别指定的, 因为不同"
"的工程可能需要使用不同版本的 Vaadin 库, 因此你必须为你的各个工程分别更新 "
"Vaadin 库."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:785
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the <filename>ivy.xml</filename> in an editor Eclipse."
msgstr "在 Eclipse 编辑器中打开 <filename>ivy.xml</filename> 文件."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the entity definition at the beginning of the file to set the Vaadin "
"version."
msgstr "在文件最前部的 entity 定义部分修改 Vaadin 版本."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;!ENTITY vaadin.version \"<emphasis role=\"bold\">7.0.1</emphasis>\"&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify either a fixed version number, as shown in the above "
"example, or a dynamic revision tag such as <literal>latest.release</"
"literal>. You can find more information about the dependency declarations in "
"Ivy documentation."
msgstr ""
"你可以象上面的例子那样指定一个固定的版本号, 也可以使用一个动态的版本号标记, "
"如 <literal>latest.release</literal>. 关于包依赖关系声明方法的更多信息, 请阅"
"读 Ivy 的文档."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click the project and select <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Resolve</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"在工程上单击鼠标右键, 选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Resolve</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Updating the libraries can take several minutes. You can see the progress in "
"the Eclipse status bar. You can get more details about the progress by "
"clicking the indicator."
msgstr ""
"版本库文件的更新过程可能需要耗费数分钟. 进度状况可以在 Eclipse 状态栏中看到. "
"点击状态栏中的指示图标可以看到进度状况的更详细信息."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have compiled the widget set for your project, recompile it by "
"clicking the <guibutton>Compile Vaadin widgets</guibutton> button in Eclipse "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"如果你曾经为你的工程编译过 widget 群, 那么 Vaadin 库版本更新后需要重新编译, "
"方法是在 Eclipse 工具栏中点击 <guibutton>Compile Vaadin widgets</guibutton> "
"按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stop the integrated Tomcat (or other server) in Eclipse, clear its caches by "
"right-clicking the server and selecting <guimenuitem>Clean</guimenuitem> as "
"well as <guimenuitem>Clean Tomcat Work Directory</guimenuitem>, and restart "
"it."
msgstr ""
"将 Eclipse 集成的 Tomcat (或者其他类型的服务器) 停止运行, 清空它的缓存, 方法"
"是在服务器上单击鼠标右键, 然后选择菜单项 <guimenuitem>Clean</guimenuitem> 和 "
"<guimenuitem>Clean Tomcat Work Directory</guimenuitem>, 然后重启服务器."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you experience problems after updating the libraries, you can try "
"clearing the Ivy resolution caches by right-clicking the project and "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clean all caches</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then, do the <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Resolve</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and other tasks "
"again."
msgstr ""
"如果更新完 Vaadin 库文件之后遭遇到问题, 你可以尝试清空 Ivy 的解析结果缓存, 方"
"法是在工程上单击鼠标右键, 然后选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Clean all caches</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. 然后重新执"
"行 <menuchoice><guimenu>Ivy</guimenu><guimenuitem>Resolve</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> 和其他操作."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and Running a Project with Eclipse"
msgstr "使用 Eclipse 创建和运行一个工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section gives instructions for creating a new Eclipse project using the "
"Vaadin Plugin. The task will include the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"本节介绍如何使用 Vaadin Plugin 创建新的 Eclipse 工程. 包括以下几个步骤:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:858
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new project"
msgstr "创建新工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write the source code"
msgstr "编写源代码"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure and start Tomcat (or some other web server)"
msgstr "配置和启动 Tomcat (或其他Web 服务器)"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:867
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a web browser to use the web application"
msgstr "打开 Web 来访问 Web 应用程序"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We also show how you can debug the application in the debug mode in Eclipse."
msgstr "我们还将介绍在 Eclipse 中如何使用 debug 模式来调试应用程序."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This walkthrough assumes that you have already installed the Vaadin Plugin "
"for Eclipse and set up your development environment, as instructed in <xref "
"linkend=\"getting-started.environment\"/>."
msgstr ""
"下面的教程假定你已经安装了 Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse, 并已配置好了你的开发环"
"境, 如 <xref linkend=\"getting-started.environment\"/> 所述."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating the Project"
msgstr "创建工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let us create the first application project with the tools installed in the "
"previous section. First, launch Eclipse and follow the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"下面让我们用前面章节中安装好的开发工具来创建我们的第一个应用程序工程. 首先, "
"启动 Eclipse, 然后执行以下步骤:"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start creating a new project by selecting from the menu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Project...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"创建一个新工程, 方法是选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Project...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> window that opens, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Web</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vaadin 7 Project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"在 <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> 窗口中, 选择菜单项 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Web</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vaadin 7 Project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> , 并点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to go the Vaadin 6 way, please use the latest Vaadin 6 version "
"of this book for further instructions."
msgstr "如果你选择 Vaadin 6 , 请阅读本书的 Vaadin 6 版."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Vaadin Project</guilabel> step, you need to set the basic "
"web project settings. You need to give at least the <emphasis>project name</"
"emphasis> and the runtime; the default values should be good for the other "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"在向导的 <guilabel>Vaadin Project</guilabel> 窗口, 你需要为 Web工程做一些基本"
"设定. 首先你至少需要指定 <emphasis>project name</emphasis> 以及这个工程使用的"
"运行环境 (runtime); 其他设定使用默认值即可."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project name"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:946
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give the project a name. The name should be a valid identifier usable cross-"
"platform as a filename and inside a URL, so using only lower-case "
"alphanumerics, underscore, and minus sign is recommended."
msgstr ""
"为工程指定一个名称. 工程名必须是一个跨平台合法的文件名, 也必须是 URL 中合法的"
"组成部分, 因此建议在工程名中只使用小写字母, 数字, 下划线, 以及横线."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use default location"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define the directory under which the project is created. The default is "
"under your workspace folder, and you should normally leave it as it is. You "
"may need to set the directory, for example, if you are creating an Eclipse "
"project on top of a version-controlled source tree."
msgstr ""
"指定工程在文件系统中的存储目录. 默认位置是在你的 workspace 文件夹下, 一般来说"
"不必修改. 但有些情况下你也许需要指定工程的存储目录, 比如, 如果你希望在版本管"
"理系统管理下的源代码树中创建 Eclipse 工程, 那么工程的位置就很重要了."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:968
#, no-c-format
msgid "Target runtime"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define the application server to use for deploying the application. The "
"server that you have installed, for example Apache Tomcat, should be "
"selected automatically. If not, click <guibutton>New</guibutton> to "
"configure a new server under Eclipse."
msgstr ""
"指定用来发布应用程序的服务器. 你安装过的服务器, 比如 Apache Tomcat, 将被自动"
"选中. 如果没有的话, 请点击 <guibutton>New</guibutton> 按钮, 可在 Eclipse 中配"
"置新的服务器."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the configuration to use; you should normally use the default "
"configuration for the application server. If you need to modify the project "
"facets, click <guibutton>Modify</guibutton>. The recommended Servlet 3.0 "
"configuration uses the @WebServlet deployment, while Servlet 2.4 uses the "
"old <filename>web.xml</filename> deployment."
msgstr ""
"选择你希望使用的配置; 一般来说应该使用应用程序服务器的默认配置. 如果你需要修"
"改 project facet, 请点击 <guibutton>Modify</guibutton> 按钮. 推荐使用 "
"Servlet 3.0 配置, 它使用 @WebServlet 进行部署,  Servlet 2.4 配置则使用老式的 "
"<filename>web.xml</filename> 进行部署."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:994
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deployment configuration"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the environment to which the application will be "
"deployed, to generate the appropriate project directory layout and "
"configuration files. The choises are:"
msgstr ""
"这个选项用于设定应用程序将被发布到的运行环境, 以便生成正确的工程目录结构及相"
"应的设定文件. 可用的选项包括:"

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Servlet</guilabel> (default)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Google App Engine Servlet"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Portlet (Portlet 2.0)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1009
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The further steps in the New Project Wizard depend on the selected "
"deployment configuration; the steps listed in this section are for the "
"default servlet configuration. <phrase condition=\"web\">See <xref linkend="
"\"advanced.gae\"/> and <xref linkend=\"portal\"/> for instructions regarding "
"the use of Vaadin in the alternative environments.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"New Project 向导的后续步骤依赖于你选择的发布配置的内容; 本节中列出的步骤只适"
"用于默认的 servlet 配置. <phrase condition=\"web\">其他几种运行环境下 Vaadin "
"的使用方法, 请参见 <xref linkend=\"advanced.gae\"/> 和 <xref linkend=\"portal"
"\"/> .</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vaadin version"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the Vaadin version to use. The drop-down list shows, by default, the "
"latest available version of Vaadin. The selection includes nightly "
"<literal>SNAPSHOT</literal> builds, if you want to keep up with the "
"absolutely latest unstable versions."
msgstr ""
"选择使用的 Vaadin 版本. 下拉框中默认选中的是 Vaadin 的最新可用版本. 如果你希"
"望随时使用最新的、非稳定版本的话, 你可以选择每夜 <literal>SNAPSHOT</literal> "
"编译版, ."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can change the version later in the <filename>ivy.xml</filename>."
msgstr "在这里选定的版本, 将来还可以在 <filename>ivy.xml</filename> 中修改."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create TestBench test"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, the application stub will include a test case for testing the "
"UI with Vaadin TestBench, as described in <xref linkend=\"testbench\"/>. "
"Vaadin TestBench API library will be included in <filename>ivy.xml</"
"filename> as a dependency. Vaadin version 7.3 or later is required to create "
"the stub."
msgstr ""
"当这个选项有效时, 自动生成的应用程序框架(stub)代码中, 将包括测试用例(test "
"case), 它将使用 Vaadin TestBench 来测试 UI, 详情请参见 <xref linkend="
"\"testbench\"/>. Vaadin TestBench API 库文件将会以一个依赖项的形式, 包含在 "
"<filename>ivy.xml</filename> 之内. 创建应用程序框架代码需要使用 Vaadin 7.3 或"
"更高版本."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> here to use the defaults for the "
"rest of the settings, or click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"如果其他所有设定都使用默认值, 可以在这一步点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> "
"按钮, 否则请点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings in the <guilabel>Web Module</guilabel> step define the basic "
"web application (WAR) deployment settings and the structure of the web "
"application project. All the settings are pre-filled, and you should "
"normally accept them as they are."
msgstr ""
"在向导的 <guilabel>Web Module</guilabel> 窗口中可以配置 Web 应用程序(WAR) 的"
"基本发布设定, 以及Web 应用程序工程的结构. 所有设定项都有预先指定的默认值, 一"
"般来说你应该这些默认设定."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Root"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context root (of the application) identifies the application in the URL "
"used for accessing it. For example, if the project has a <literal>myproject</"
"literal> context and a single UI at the context root, the URL would be "
"<uri>http://example.com/myproject</uri>. The wizard will suggest the project "
"name given in the first step as the context name. You can change the context "
"root later in the Eclipse project properties."
msgstr ""
"应用程序的 context root 指定了访问应用程序时的 URL. 比如, 如果工程的 context "
"被设定为 <literal>myproject</literal>, 并且只有一个唯一的 UI, 那么 URL 将是 "
"<uri>http://example.com/myproject</uri>. 向导默认使用第一步中指定的工程名作"
"为 context 名. 你将来可以在 Eclipse 工程的属性中修改 context root."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content Directory"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The directory containing all the content to be included in the web "
"application (WAR) that is deployed to the web server. The directory is "
"relative to the root directory of the project."
msgstr ""
"指定一个目录名, 这个目录之下的一切内容都将被包含到 Web 应用程序(WAR) 中, 然后"
"被发布到 Web 服务器上. 这里输入的目录是从工程根路径开始的相对路径."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can just accept the defaults and click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr "你可以使用默认设定, 点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Vaadin project</guilabel> step page has various Vaadin-"
"specific application settings. If you are trying out Vaadin for the first "
"time, you should not need to change anything. You can set most of the "
"settings afterwards, except the creation of the portlet configuration."
msgstr ""
"向导的 <guilabel>Vaadin project</guilabel> 窗口包括一些 Vaadin 专有的设定内"
"容. 如果你是初次使用 Vaadin, 建议不要修改默认设定. 大多数设定项都可以留在将来"
"再修改, 只有 portlet 相关设定除外."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create project template"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make the wizard create an UI class stub."
msgstr "让向导帮你创建 UI 类的基本框架."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Name"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A name for the application UI, shown in the title bar of the browser window."
msgstr "应用程序 UI 的名称, 将显示在浏览器窗口的标题栏中."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base package name"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the Java package under which the UI class of the application is "
"to be placed."
msgstr "Java 包的名称, 应用程序 UI 类将被置于这个包之下."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application/UI class name"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the UI class for the application, in which the user interface is "
"developed."
msgstr "应用程序 UI 类的名称, 应用程序的 UI 代码将在这个 UI 类中开发."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Portlet version"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a portlet version is selected (only Portlet 2.0 is supported), the "
"wizard will create the files needed for running the application in a portal. "
"See <xref linkend=\"portal\"/> for more information on portlets."
msgstr ""
"当 portlet 版本有指定时 (只支持 Portlet 2.0), 向导将创建应用程序在 portal 中"
"运行时所需要的文件. 关于 portlet 的详情请参见 <xref linkend=\"portal\"/> ."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finally, click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> to create the project."
msgstr "最后, 点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 即可创建工程."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exploring the Project"
msgstr "浏览一下工程结构"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> wizard exits, it has done all the "
"work for you: an UI class skeleton has been written to <filename>src</"
"filename> directory and the <filename>WebContent/WEB-INF/web.xml</filename> "
"contains a deployment descriptor. The project hierarchy shown in the Project "
"Explorer is shown in <xref linkend=\"figure.getting-started.first-project."
"exploring\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>New Project</guilabel> 向导运行完成后, 它将为你完成所有工作: UI 类"
"的基本框架已经生成到 <filename>src</filename> 目录下, <filename>WebContent/"
"WEB-INF/web.xml</filename> 文件中已经包含了应用程序的部署描述信息. Eclipse "
"的 Project Explorer 视图中显示的工程层级结构参见 <xref linkend=\"figure."
"getting-started.first-project.exploring\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "A New Vaadin Project"
msgstr "一个新的 Vaadin 工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vaadin libraries and other dependencies are managed by Ivy. Notice that "
"the libraries are not stored under the project folder, even though they are "
"listed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Java Resources</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Libraries</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>ivy.xml</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> virtual folder."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 库以及工程依赖的其他包由 Ivy 负责管理. 注意, 库文件并没有存储到工程文"
"件夹之内, 但它们仍然被显示在虚拟文件夹 <menuchoice><guimenu>Java Resources</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Libraries</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>ivy.xml</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> 之下."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1223
#, no-c-format
msgid "The UI Class"
msgstr "UI 类"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid "The UI class created by the plugin contains the following code:"
msgstr "插件自动创建的 UI 类包含以下代码:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<?pocket-size 65% ?><![CDATA[package com.example.myproject;\n"
"\n"
"import com.vaadin.ui.UI;\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"@SuppressWarnings(\"serial\")\n"
"@Theme(\"myproject\")\n"
"public class MyprojectUI extends UI {\n"
"\n"
"    @WebServlet(value = \"/*\", asyncSupported = true)\n"
"    @VaadinServletConfiguration(\n"
"            productionMode = false,\n"
"            ui = MyprojectUI.class)\n"
"    public static class Servlet extends VaadinServlet {\n"
"    }\n"
"\n"
"    @Override\n"
"    protected void init(VaadinRequest request) {\n"
"        final VerticalLayout layout = new VerticalLayout();\n"
"        layout.setMargin(true);\n"
"        setContent(layout);\n"
"\n"
"        Button button = new Button(\"Click Me\");\n"
"        button.addClickListener(new Button.ClickListener() {\n"
"            public void buttonClick(ClickEvent event) {\n"
"                layout.addComponent(\n"
"                    new Label(\"Thank you for clicking\"));\n"
"            }\n"
"        });\n"
"        layout.addComponent(button);\n"
"    }\n"
"}]]>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a Servlet 3.0 project, the deployment is configured with servlet class "
"and a <literal>@WebServlet</literal> annotation. The stub includes the "
"servlet class as a static inner class. You may want to refactor it to a "
"separate normal class."
msgstr ""
"在 Servlet 3.0 工程中, 部署的配置使用 servlet 类, 以及一个 "
"<literal>@WebServlet</literal> 标注. 插件创建的框架代码中包含一个 servlet "
"类, 但是是static inner 类的形式. 如果你希望, 也可以将它重构为一个单独的一般"
"类."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a Servlet 2.3 project, you would have a <filename>web.xml</filename> "
"deployment descriptor."
msgstr ""
"对于 Servlet 2.3 工程, 你将得到一个 <filename>web.xml</filename> 部署描述文"
"件."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a more detailed treatment of the deployment, see <xref linkend="
"\"application.environment.web-xml\"/>."
msgstr ""
"关于发布的详细信息, 请参见 <xref linkend=\"application.environment.web-xml\"/"
">."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coding Tips for Eclipse"
msgstr "针对 Eclipse 的编码提示"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the most useful features in Eclipse is <emphasis>code completion</"
"emphasis>. Pressing <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Space</keycap></"
"keycombo> in the editor will display a popup list of possible class name and "
"method name completions, as shown in <xref linkend=\"figure.getting-started."
"first-project.coding.codecompletion\"/>, depending on the context of the "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Eclipse 最有用的功能之一就是 <emphasis>自动代码补完</emphasis>. 在编辑器中按"
"下 <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo> 键, 将弹"
"出一个下拉列表,  其中包括所有可能的类名或方法名的补完提示, 参见 <xref "
"linkend=\"figure.getting-started.first-project.coding.codecompletion\"/>, 自"
"动补完提示的内容将根据目前光标所在位置的源代码上下文而不同."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Java Code Completion in Eclipse"
msgstr "Eclipse 中的 Java 源代码自动补完功能"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add an <literal>import</literal> statement for a class, such as "
"<classname>Button</classname>, simply press <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> or click the red "
"error indicator on the left side of the editor window. If the class is "
"available in multiple packages, a list of the alternatives is displayed, as "
"shown in <xref linkend=\"figure.getting-started.first-project.coding.import"
"\"/>. For server-side development, you should normally use the classes under "
"the <package>com.vaadin.ui</package> or <package>com.vaadin.server</package> "
"packages. You can not use client-side classes (under <package>com.vaadin."
"client</package>) or GWT classes for server-side development."
msgstr ""
"要向一个类添加一条 <literal>import</literal> 语句, 比如 <classname>Button</"
"classname>, 只需要按下 <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Shift</"
"keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> 键, 或者在编辑器窗口的左侧点击红色的错误"
"提示图标. 如果希望引入的类存在于多个包中, 将会出现一个选项列表, 参见 <xref "
"linkend=\"figure.getting-started.first-project.coding.import\"/>. 对于服务器"
"端开发, 一般应该使用 <package>com.vaadin.ui</package> 或 <package>com.vaadin."
"server</package> 包下的类. 你不能将客户端类(位于 <package>com.vaadin.client</"
"package> 包之下) 或 GWT 类用于服务器端开发."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Classes Automatically"
msgstr "自动导入 Java 类"

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting Up and Starting the Web Server"
msgstr "配置和启动 Web 服务器"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers has the Web Standard Tools package "
"installed, which supports control of various web servers and automatic "
"deployment of web content to the server when changes are made to a project."
msgstr ""
"Eclipse IDE for Java EE Developers 包含了 WST (Web Standard Tools), WST 可以"
"管理多种 Web 服务器, 当工程中文件发生变化时, WST 可以将 Web 内容自动发布到服"
"务器中."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that Tomcat was installed with user permissions. Configuration of "
"the web server in Eclipse will fail if the user does not have write "
"permissions to the configuration and deployment directories under the Tomcat "
"installation directory."
msgstr ""
"请确认 Tomcat 是在一般用户权限下安装的. 如果运行 Eclipse 的用户对 Tomcat 安装"
"目录下的配置和发布目录没有写入权限, 在 Eclipse 中配置 Web 服务器时将会失败."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Follow the following steps."
msgstr "然后请执行以下几步."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to the <guimenuitem>Servers</guimenuitem> tab in the lower panel in "
"Eclipse. List of servers should be empty after Eclipse is installed. Right-"
"click on the empty area in the panel and select <menuchoice><guimenu>New</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Server</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"在 Eclipse 下方窗口栏中切换到 <guimenuitem>Servers</guimenuitem> 页. Eclipse "
"初期安装完毕时, 这个窗口中显示的服务器列表将是空的. 在窗口的空白位置点击鼠标"
"右键, 选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>New</guimenu><guimenuitem>Server</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Apache</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tomcat v7.0 Server</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and set <guilabel>Server's host name</guilabel> as "
"<literal>localhost</literal>, which should be the default. If you have only "
"one Tomcat installed, <guilabel>Server runtime</guilabel> has only one "
"choice. Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Apache</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tomcat v7.0 Server</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> , 然后将 <guilabel>Server's host name</guilabel> 设"
"置为 <literal>localhost</literal>, 默认值就是如此. 如果你的系统中只安装过一"
"份 Tomcat, <guilabel>Server runtime</guilabel> 将只有唯一一个可选项. 点击 "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add your project to the server by selecting it on the left and clicking "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> to add it to the configured projects on the "
"right. Click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"将你的工程添加到服务器中, 方法是在左侧列表中选中工程, 然后点击 "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> 按钮, 将它追加到右侧的 Configured 工程列表. 然后点"
"击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The server and the project are now installed in Eclipse and are shown in the "
"<guilabel>Servers</guilabel> tab. To start the server, right-click on the "
"server and select <guimenuitem>Debug</guimenuitem>. To start the server in "
"non-debug mode, select <guimenuitem>Start</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"至此, 服务器与工程都已在 Eclipse 中设置完毕, 将显示在 <guilabel>Servers</"
"guilabel> 窗口中. 要启动服务器, 请在服务器上点击鼠标右键， 选择菜单项 "
"<guimenuitem>Debug</guimenuitem>. 如果要在非 debug 模式下启动服务器, 请选择菜"
"单项 <guimenuitem>Start</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: listitem
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The server starts and the WebContent directory of the project is published "
"to the server on <uri>http://localhost:8080/myproject/</uri>."
msgstr ""
"服务器将开始运行,  工程的 WebContent 目录将被发布到服务器上, 其地址为 "
"<uri>http://localhost:8080/myproject/</uri>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running and Debugging"
msgstr "运行和调试"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starting your application is as easy as selecting <guilabel>myproject</"
"guilabel> from the <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> and then "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Debug As</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Debug on Server</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Eclipse "
"then opens the application in built-in web browser."
msgstr ""
"运行应用程序是很容易的, 方法是在 <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> 窗口中"
"选择 <guilabel>myproject</guilabel>, 然后选择菜单项 "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Debug As</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Debug on Server</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Eclipse "
"会在它的内嵌 Web 浏览器中打开应用程序."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running a Vaadin Application"
msgstr "运行 Vaadin 应用程序"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert break points in the Java code by double-clicking on the left "
"margin bar of the source code window. For example, if you insert a "
"breakpoint in the <methodname>buttonClick()</methodname> method and click "
"the <guibutton>What is the time?</guibutton> button, Eclipse will ask to "
"switch to the Debug perspective. Debug perspective will show where the "
"execution stopped at the breakpoint. You can examine and change the state of "
"the application. To continue execution, select <guimenuitem>Resume</"
"guimenuitem> from <guimenu>Run</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 Java 代码中设置断点, 方法是源代码编辑器窗口左侧空白位置双击鼠标. 比"
"如, 如果你在 <methodname>buttonClick()</methodname> 方法上添加断点, 然后在浏"
"览器中点击 <guibutton>What is the time?</guibutton> 按钮, Eclipse 将询问是否"
"切换到 Debug 透视图(perspective) . Debug 透视图将显示当前程序的运行停止在断点"
"的何处. 此时你可以查看应用程序的各种状态, 也可以修改这些状态. 要继续程序的运"
"行, 请从 <guimenu>Run</guimenu> 菜单中选择菜单项 <guimenuitem>Resume</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debugging a Vaadin Application"
msgstr "调试 Vaadin 应用程序"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above, we described how to debug a server-side application. Debugging client-"
"side applications and widgets is described in <xref linkend=\"clientside."
"debugging\"/>."
msgstr ""
"上文我们介绍了如何调试服务器端应用程序. 客户端应用程序和 widget 的调试方法参"
"见 <xref linkend=\"clientside.debugging\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Vaadin with Maven"
msgstr "通过 Maven 使用 Vaadin"

#. Tag: primary
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1469 chapter-getting-started.xml:1651
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maven"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: secondary
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1470
#, no-c-format
msgid "creating a project"
msgstr "创建工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maven is a commonly used build and dependency management system. The Vaadin "
"core library and all Vaadin add-ons are available through Maven. You can use "
"a Maven with a front-end from Eclipse or NetBeans, or by using the command-"
"line as described in this section."
msgstr ""
"Maven 是一个被广泛使用的构建和包依赖管理系统. Vaadin 核心库以及所有的 Vaadin "
"插件都可以通过 Maven 得到. 你可以将 Eclipse 或 NetBeans 中作为前端工具来使用 "
"Maven, 或者也可以通过命令行来使用 Maven, 详情见本节余下内容."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to regular Maven, you can use any Maven-compatible build or "
"dependency management system, such as Ivy or Gradle. For Gradle, see the "
"<link xlink:href=\"https://github.com/johndevs/gradle-vaadin-plugin\">Gradle "
"Vaadin Plugin</link>. Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse uses Ivy for resolving "
"dependencies in Vaadin projects, and it should provide you with the basic "
"Ivy configuration."
msgstr ""
"除了通常的 Maven 方式外, 你还可以任何一种与 Maven 兼容的构建和包依赖管理系"
"统, 比如 Ivy 或 Gradle. 关于 Gradle 的使用, 参见 <link xlink:href=\"https://"
"github.com/johndevs/gradle-vaadin-plugin\">Gradle Vaadin Plugin</link>. "
"Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse 使用 Ivy 来为 Vaadin 工程解析它的包依赖关系, "
"Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse 还会为你提供基本的 Ivy 配置."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working from Command-Line"
msgstr "通过命令行使用 Maven"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a new Maven project with the following command (given in one "
"line):"
msgstr "你可以通过以下命令新建一个 Maven 工程:"

#. Tag: screen
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>$</prompt> <command>mvn</command> archetype:generate\n"
"   -DarchetypeGroupId=com.vaadin\n"
"   -DarchetypeArtifactId=<parameter>vaadin-archetype-application</"
"parameter>\n"
"   -DarchetypeVersion=<parameter>&version.vaadin;</parameter>\n"
"   -DgroupId=<parameter>your.company</parameter>\n"
"   -DartifactId=<parameter>project-name</parameter>\n"
"   -Dversion=<parameter>1.0</parameter>\n"
"   -Dpackaging=war"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid "The parameters are as follows:"
msgstr "各参数的说明如下:"

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1506
#, no-c-format
msgid "archetypeGroupId"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The group ID of the archetype is <literal>com.vaadin</literal> for Vaadin "
"archetypes."
msgstr ""
"指定 archetype 的 group ID, 对 Vaadin archetype, 应该设置为 <literal>com."
"vaadin</literal>."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1515
#, no-c-format
msgid "archetypeArtifactId"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The archetype ID. Vaadin 7 currently supports <literal>vaadin-archetype-"
"application</literal> archetype for server-side applications and "
"<literal>vaadin-archetype-widget</literal> for client-side widget "
"development projects."
msgstr ""
"指定 archetype ID. Vaadin 7 目前支持 <literal>vaadin-archetype-application</"
"literal>, 用于服务器端应用程序工程, 以及 <literal>vaadin-archetype-widget</"
"literal>, 用于客户端 widget 工程."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid "archetypeVersion"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Version of the archetype to use. This should be <literal>LATEST</literal> "
"for normal Vaadin releases. For prerelease versions it should be the exact "
"version number, such as <literal>7.0.0.beta3</literal>."
msgstr ""
"指定 archetype 的版本. 对于一般的 Vaadin 发行版, 应该使用 <literal>LATEST</"
"literal>. 对于预发布版应该使用明确的版本号, 比如 <literal>7.0.0.beta3</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1583
#, no-c-format
msgid "groupId"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Maven group ID for your project. It is normally your organization domain "
"name in reverse order, such as <uri>com.example</uri>. The group ID is also "
"used as a prefix for the Java package in the sources, so it should be Java "
"compatible - only alphanumerics and an underscore."
msgstr ""
"指定你的工程的 Maven group ID. 一般来说应该使用你所属组织的域名的反序, 比如 "
"<uri>com.example</uri>. group ID 还被用作你工程源代码中的 Java 包名前缀, 所以"
"它必须是合法的 Java 包名 - 其中只能使用字母, 数字, 以及下划线."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid "artifactId"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifier of the artifact, that is, your project. The identifier may "
"contain alphanumerics, minus, and underscore. It is appended to the group ID "
"to obtain the Java package name for the sources. For example, if the group "
"ID is <uri>com.example</uri> and artifact ID is <uri>myproject</uri>, the "
"project sources would be placed in <uri>com.example.myproject</uri> package."
msgstr ""
"artifact (也就是你的工程)的 ID. 这个 ID 可以包含字母, 数字, 横线, 以及下划"
"线. 它将添加到 group ID 之后, 组成源代码中的 Java 包名称. 比如, 如果 group "
"ID 是 <uri>com.example</uri>, artifact ID 是 <uri>myproject</uri>, 那么工程的"
"源代码将被放在 <uri>com.example.myproject</uri> 包之下."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1609
#, no-c-format
msgid "version"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Initial version number of your application. The number must obey the Maven "
"version numbering format."
msgstr "指定你应用程序的初始版本号. 版本号必须遵守 Maven 版本号格式规则."

#. Tag: parameter
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid "packaging"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How will the project be packaged. It is normally <literal>war</literal>."
msgstr "指定你的工程的打包方式. 通常使用 <literal>war</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a project can take a while as Maven fetches all the dependencies. "
"The created project structure is shown in <xref linkend=\"figure.getting-"
"started.maven.archetype.created\"/>."
msgstr ""
"创建工程可能会耗费一些时间, 因为 Maven 需要下载所有的依赖包. 创建出来的工程结"
"构参见 <xref linkend=\"figure.getting-started.maven.archetype.created\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid "A New Vaadin Project with Maven"
msgstr "使用 Maven 新建的 Vaadin 工程"

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compiling and Running the Application"
msgstr "编译和运行应用程序"

#. Tag: secondary
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid "compiling"
msgstr "编译"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before the application can be deployed, it must be compiled and packaged as "
"a WAR package. You can do this with the <literal>package</literal> goal as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"应用程序发布之前, 它必须编译并打包为 WAR 形式. 你可以运行 Maven 的 "
"<literal>package</literal> 目标(goal)来执行编译和打包任务, 方法如下:"

#. Tag: screen
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <command>mvn</command> package"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the resulting WAR package should be displayed in the command "
"output. You can then deploy it to your favorite application server."
msgstr ""
"最终打包完成的 WAR 包文件的位置, 将输出到命令行中. 然后你就可以将这个 WAR 包"
"文件发布到你喜欢的应用程序服务器了."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to run Vaadin applications with Maven is to use the light-"
"weight Jetty web server. After compiling the package, all you need to do is "
"type:"
msgstr ""
"通过 Maven 运行 Vaadin 应用程序的最简便方法是使用轻量的 Jetty Web 服务器. 编"
"译完成后, 你需要做的仅仅是:"

#. Tag: screen
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1675
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <command>mvn</command> jetty:run"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The special goal starts the Jetty server in port 8080 and deploys the "
"application. You can then open it in a web browser at <uri>http://"
"localhost:8080/project-name</uri>."
msgstr ""
"上述 Maven 目标(goal) 会在 8080 端口上启动 Jetty 服务器, 然后将应用程序部署到"
"服务器上. 然后你可以在浏览器中打开应用程序, 地址是 <uri>http://"
"localhost:8080/project-name</uri>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Add-ons and Custom Widget Sets"
msgstr "使用插件和定制 Widget 群"

#. Tag: secondary
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1691
#, no-c-format
msgid "using add-ons"
msgstr "使用插件"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use Vaadin add-ons that include a widget set or make your custom "
"widgets, you need to enable widget set compilation in the POM. The required "
"configuration is described in <xref linkend=\"addons.maven\"/>."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用了包含 widget 群的 Vaadin 插件, 或者希望创建自定义的 widget, 你需要"
"在 POM 设定文件中打开 widget 群的编译功能. 详细的设定方法参见 <xref linkend="
"\"addons.maven\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Project with NetBeans IDE"
msgstr "使用 NetBeans IDE 创建工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to develop Vaadin application with the NetBeans IDE is to "
"use the Vaadin Plugin for NetBeans. It allows you to create new Vaadin "
"projects easily and provides many features for working on a project. You can "
"download the plugin at <link xlink:href=\"http://plugins.netbeans.org/"
"plugin/50531/vaadin-plug-in-for-netbeans\">http://plugins.netbeans.org/"
"plugin/50531/vaadin-plug-in-for-netbeans</link>. The download page contains "
"a link to a plugin features overview in NetBeans Wiki."
msgstr ""
"在 NetBeans IDE 中开发 Vaadin 应用程序的最简便方法是使用 Vaadin Plugin for "
"NetBeans . 这个插件可以帮助你便利地创建 Vaadin 工程, 还提供了很多其他功能. 插"
"件可在以下地址下载: <link xlink:href=\"http://plugins.netbeans.org/"
"plugin/50531/vaadin-plug-in-for-netbeans\">http://plugins.netbeans.org/"
"plugin/50531/vaadin-plug-in-for-netbeans</link>. 下载页面还包括一个链接, 指向"
"该插件功能概要介绍的 NetBeans Wiki 页面."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Without the plugin, you can most easily create a Vaadin project as a Maven "
"project using a Vaadin archetype. You can also create a Vaadin project as a "
"regular web application project, but it requires many manual steps to "
"install all the Vaadin libraries, create the UI class, configure the "
"servlet, create theme, and so on."
msgstr ""
"不使用上述插件的话, 最简便方法是以\"使用 Vaadin Archetype 的Maven 工程\"方式"
"来创建 Vaadin 工程. 也可以作为通常的 Web 应用程序来创建, 但这种方式需要很多手"
"工步骤来安装 Vaadin 库, 创建 UI 类, 配置 Servlet, 创建 theme, 等等等等."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maven Project from a Vaadin Archetype"
msgstr "使用 Vaadin Archetype 的Maven 工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a Maven project with a Vaadin archetype creates an application "
"skeleton with a UI class and project theme, defines the <filename>web.xml</"
"filename> deployment descriptor, and also retrieves the latest Vaadin "
"library automatically."
msgstr ""
"创建 Vaadin archetype 的 Maven 工程, 将自动生成应用程序的基本框架, 包括 UI 类"
"和工程的 theme, 还会自动定义 <filename>web.xml</filename> 部署描述文件, 而且"
"还将自动取得最新版本的 Vaadin 库."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Project</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1742
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Maven</guimenu><guimenuitem>Project from "
"Archetype</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Maven</guimenu><guimenuitem>Project from "
"Archetype</guimenuitem></menuchoice> , 然后点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> "
"按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find <literal>vaadin-archetype-application</literal>, select it, and click "
"<guilabel>Next</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"找到 <literal>vaadin-archetype-application</literal>, 选中它, 然后点击 "
"<guilabel>Next</guilabel> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Name and Location</guilabel> step, enter <guilabel>Project "
"Name</guilabel>, which is recommended to be only lower-case alphabetics, as "
"it is used also as a suggestion for the Java package name of the project. "
"Modify the other parameters for your project and click <guibutton>Finish</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"在向导的 <guilabel>Name and Location</guilabel> 窗口, 输入 <guilabel>Project "
"Name</guilabel>, 建议只是使用小写英文字母, 因为它也会被用作工程内 Java 包名. "
"修改其他设定参数, 然后点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a New Maven Project in NetBeans"
msgstr "在 NetBeans 中添加新的 Maven 工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating the project can take a while as Maven loads all the needed "
"dependencies. Once created, you can run it by right-clicking on the project "
"in the <guilabel>Projects</guilabel> view and selecting <guilabel>Run</"
"guilabel>. In the <guilabel>Select deployment server</guilabel> window that "
"opens, select <guilabel>Glassfish</guilabel> or <guilabel>Apache Tomcat</"
"guilabel>, and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. If all goes well, NetBeans "
"starts the server in port 8080 and, depending on your system configuration, "
"launches the default browser to display the web application. If not, you can "
"open it manually, for example, at <uri>http://localhost:8080/myproject</"
"uri>. The project name is used by default as the context path of the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"创建工程可能需要耗费一些时间, 因为 Maven 需要装载所有依赖到的包. 创建完成后, "
"你可以通过 <guilabel>Projects</guilabel> 窗口, 在工程上点击鼠标右键, 然后选择"
"菜单项 <guilabel>Run</guilabel> 来运行工程. 这里将出现 <guilabel>Select "
"deployment server</guilabel> 窗口, 请在这个窗口中选择 <guilabel>Glassfish</"
"guilabel> 或 <guilabel>Apache Tomcat</guilabel>, 然后点击 <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> 按钮. 如果一切顺利的话, NetBeans 将在 8080 端口上启动服务器, 然后"
"打开默认浏览器来显示你的 Web 程序. 默认浏览器是什么, 取决于你的操作系统设定. "
"如果 Web 程序未能自动显示, 你可以手动访问它, 地址是 <uri>http://"
"localhost:8080/myproject</uri>. 默认情况下, 工程名称会被使用为应用程序的 "
"context  路径."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Project with IntelliJ IDEA"
msgstr "使用 IntelliJ IDEA 创建工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Ultimate Edition of IntelliJ IDEA includes support for creating Vaadin "
"applications and running or debugging them in an integrated application "
"server. With the Community Edition, you can create a Vaadin application most "
"easily with a Maven archetype and deploy it to a server with a Maven run/"
"debug configuration."
msgstr ""
"IntelliJ IDEA 的 Ultimate 版支持创建 Vaadin 应用程序, 还可以在集成的应用程序"
"服务器中运行或调试它. 如果使用 Community 版, 创建 Vaadin 应用程序的最简便方法"
"是创建 Vaadin Archetype 的 Maven 工程, 然后通过 Maven 的 run/debug 配置将应用"
"程序发布到服务器上."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, see the article \"<link xlink:href=\"http://wiki."
"jetbrains.net/intellij/"
"Creating_a_simple_Web_application_and_deploying_it_to_Tomcat\">Creating a "
"simple Web application and deploying it to Tomcat</link>\" in the IntelliJ "
"IDEA Encyclopedia wiki."
msgstr ""
"详情请到 IntelliJ IDEA 百科全书 WIKI 系统阅读以下文章, \"<link xlink:href="
"\"http://wiki.jetbrains.net/intellij/"
"Creating_a_simple_Web_application_and_deploying_it_to_Tomcat\">Creating a "
"simple Web application and deploying it to Tomcat</link>\"."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring an Application Server"
msgstr "配置应用程序服务器"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application during development in the Ultimate Edition of "
"IntelliJ IDEA, you first need to install and configure an application server "
"that is integrated with the IDE. The edition includes integration with many "
"commonly used application servers."
msgstr ""
"在 IntelliJ IDEA 的 Ultimate 版中运行应用程序, 首先需要安装和配置与 IDE 集成"
"的应用程序服务器. IntelliJ IDEA 的 Ultimate 版集成了很多常用的应用程序服务器."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1821
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the following, we configure Apache Tomcat:"
msgstr "在本示例中我们配置 Apache Tomcat, 步骤如下:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download and extract Tomcat installation package to a local directory, as "
"instructed in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.environment.tomcat\"/>."
msgstr ""
"下载 Tomcat 安装包, 并解压缩到适当的本地目录, 详情参见 <xref linkend="
"\"getting-started.environment.tomcat\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guimenuitem>Settings</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guimenuitem>Settings</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>IDE Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Application "
"Servers</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>IDE Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Application "
"Servers</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>+</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tomcat Server</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to add a Tomcat server, or any of the other "
"supported servers. A WebSocket-enabled server, such as Glassfish or TomEE, "
"is required for server push."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>+</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tomcat Server</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, 添加一个 Tomcat 服务器, 也可以选择其他服务器类型. "
"注意, 对于服务器端 PUSH 功能, 需要使用支持 WebSocket 的服务器, 比如 "
"Glassfish 或 TomEE."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1855
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the Tomcat Server dialog, specify the home directory for the server."
msgstr "在 Tomcat Server 对话框中, 指定服务器的 home 目录."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1868 chapter-getting-started.xml:2228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr "点击 <guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1875
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review the application server settings page to check that it is OK."
msgstr "复查应用程序服务器的设定内容是否正确."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1888
#, no-c-format
msgid "Then, click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr "然后点击 <guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Vaadin Web Application Project"
msgstr "创建 Vaadin Web 应用程序工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1898
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the welcome page, do the following:"
msgstr "在 Welcome 页中, 进行如下操作:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download and exctract the Vaadin installation package to a local folder, as "
"instructed in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.package\"/>."
msgstr ""
"下载 Vaadin 安装包, 解压缩到本地目录, 详情参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-"
"started.package\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1910 chapter-getting-started.xml:2042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <menuchoice><guimenu>New Project</guimenu></menuchoice>"
msgstr "选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>New Project</guimenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> window, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Java</guimenu></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"在 <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> 窗口, 选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Java</"
"guimenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a <guilabel>Project name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Project location</"
"guilabel>, and select the <guilabel>Java SDK</guilabel> to be used for the "
"project. Vaadin requires at least Java 6. If you have not configured a Java "
"SDK previously, you can configure it here."
msgstr ""
"输入 <guilabel>Project name</guilabel> 和 <guilabel>Project location</"
"guilabel>, 然后选择工程使用的 <guilabel>Java SDK</guilabel>. Vaadin 需要 "
"Java 6 以上版本. 如果你没有预先配置 Java SDK, 你可以在这个界面中配置它."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1939 chapter-getting-started.xml:2131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr "点击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Application</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vaadin</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to add Vaadin technology to the project."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Application</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vaadin</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, 将 Vaadin 追加到工程中."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select Vaadin <guilabel>Version</guilabel> and <guilabel>Distribution</"
"guilabel> installation path. You probably also want an application stub, so "
"select <guilabel>Create sample application</guilabel> and give a name for "
"the generated UI class."
msgstr ""
"选择 Vaadin <guilabel>Version</guilabel> 和 <guilabel>Distribution</"
"guilabel> 安装路径. 你可能希望自动生成应用程序框架, 请选择 <guilabel>Create "
"sample application</guilabel> , 并指定 UI 类的名称."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do <emphasis>not</emphasis> click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> yet."
msgstr ""
"这里暂时 <emphasis>不要</emphasis> 点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Application Server</guilabel> in the same window. Set it as "
"an integrated server that you have configured in IntelliJ IDEA, as described "
"previously in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.idea.server\"/>."
msgstr ""
"在同一个窗口中选择 <guilabel>Application Server</guilabel>. 将它设置为与 "
"IntelliJ IDEA 集成的服务器, 服务器的配置方法参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-"
"started.idea.server\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr "点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The project is created with the UI class stub and a <filename>web.xml</"
"filename> deployment descriptor."
msgstr ""
"工程创建完成, 其中包含 UI 类的框架, 以及 <filename>web.xml</filename> 部署描"
"述文件."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wizard does not currently create a servlet class automatically, and uses "
"Servlet 2.4 compatible deployment with a <filename>web.xml</filename> "
"deployment descriptor."
msgstr ""
"向导目前还不能自动生成 Servlet 类, 而且它目前使用的还是  Servlet 2.4 规格的部"
"署方式, 部署设定由 <filename>web.xml</filename> 文件指定."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2017
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deploying the Project"
msgstr "发布工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To deploy the application to the integrated web server, right-click the "
"<filename>index.jsp</filename> file in the project and select "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Run 'index.jsp'</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This "
"starts the integrated server, if it was not already running, and launches "
"the default browser with the application page."
msgstr ""
"要将应用程序发布到集成的 Web 服务器上, 请在工程内的 <filename>index.jsp</"
"filename> 文件上点击鼠标右键, 然后选择菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Run "
"'index.jsp'</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. 如果集成的服务器尚未启动的话, 以上操"
"作将启动它,  并将在默认的浏览器内打开应用程序页面."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2031
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Maven Project"
msgstr "创建 Maven 工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to create a Maven project in IntelliJ IDEA. This is the "
"recommended way when using the Community Edition. You will not have the "
"application server integration, but can deploy the application to an "
"application server using a run/debug configuration."
msgstr ""
"你也可以在 IntelliJ IDEA 中创建 Maven 工程. 当使用 IntelliJ IDEA 的 "
"Community 版时, 推荐使用这种方式. 这种方式将不会与应用程序服务器自动集成, 但"
"可以使用 run/debug 配置将应用程序发布到服务器上."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> window, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Maven</guimenu></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"在 <guilabel>New Project</guilabel> 窗口中, 选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Maven</"
"guimenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a project name, location, and the Java SDK to be used for the project. "
"Vaadin requires at least Java 6. Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"输入工程名, 位置, 以及工程使用的 Java SDK . Vaadin 需要 Java 6 以上版本. 点"
"击 <guibutton>Next</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give a Maven <guilabel>GroupID</guilabel>, <guilabel>ArtifactID</guilabel>, "
"and a <guilabel>Version</guilabel> for the project, or use the defaults."
msgstr ""
"为工程指定 Maven <guilabel>GroupID</guilabel>, <guilabel>ArtifactID</"
"guilabel>, 以及 <guilabel>Version</guilabel>, 这些项目都可以使用默认值."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2088
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check <guilabel>Create from archetype</guilabel>"
msgstr "选中 <guilabel>Create from archetype</guilabel> 选项"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the Vaadin archetype is not in the list, click <guibutton>Add archetype</"
"guibutton>, enter <guilabel>GroupId</guilabel> <literal>com.vaadin</"
"literal>, <guilabel>ArtifactId</guilabel> <literal>vaadin-archetype-"
"application</literal>, and <guilabel>Version</guilabel> <literal>LATEST</"
"literal> (or a specific version number)."
msgstr ""
"如果选项列表中不包含 Vaadin archetype , 点击 <guibutton>Add archetype</"
"guibutton> 按钮, 输入 <guilabel>GroupId</guilabel> <literal>com.vaadin</"
"literal>, <guilabel>ArtifactId</guilabel> <literal>vaadin-archetype-"
"application</literal>, 以及 <guilabel>Version</guilabel> <literal>LATEST</"
"literal> (也可以指定某个具体的版本号)."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> in the dialog."
msgstr "点击对话框的 <guibutton>OK</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the <literal>com.vaadin:vaadin-archetype-application</literal>."
msgstr "选择 <literal>com.vaadin:vaadin-archetype-application</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Review the general Maven settings and settings for the new project. You may "
"need to override the settings, especially if you are creating a Maven "
"project for the first time. Click <guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"为你的新工程复查 Maven 的通用设定项, 以及工程专有的设定项. 你可能需要修改某些"
"设定, 尤其是当你初次创建 Maven 工程时. 点击 <guibutton>Finish</guibutton> 按"
"钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating the Maven project takes some time as Maven fetches the "
"dependencies. Once done, the project is created and the Maven POM is opened "
"in the editor."
msgstr ""
"创建 Maven 工程将耗费一些时间, 因为 Maven 需要下载所有的依赖包. 完成之后, 工"
"程将被创建出来, Maven POM 将在编辑器中打开."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compiling the Project"
msgstr "编译工程"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To compile a Vaadin application using Maven, you can define a run/debug "
"configuration to execute a goal such as <literal>package</literal> to build "
"the deployable WAR package. It will also compile the widget set and theme, "
"if necessary. See <xref linkend=\"getting-started.maven.compiling\"/> for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"要使用 Maven 编译 Vaadin 应用程序, 你可以定义一个 run/debug 配置项来执行 "
"Maven 目标(goal), 比如 <literal>package</literal>, 来构建一个可发布的 WAR "
"包. 如果需要的话, 它还会编译 widget 群和theme. 详情参见 <xref linkend="
"\"getting-started.maven.compiling\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compilation is included in the following instructions for deploying the "
"application."
msgstr "以下操作手顺介绍如何发布应用程序, 其中也包括如何编译应用程序."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deploying to a Server"
msgstr "发布到服务器"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There exists Maven plugins for deploying to various application servers. For "
"example, to deploy to Apache Tomcat, you can to configure the "
"<literal>tomcat-maven-plugin</literal> and then execute the <literal>tomcat:"
"deploy</literal> goal. See the documentation of the plugin that you use for "
"more details. If no Maven plugin exists for a particular server, you can "
"always use some lower-level method to deploy the application, such as "
"running an Ant task."
msgstr ""
"有很多 Maven 插件, 可用于发布应用程序到各种类型的服务器. 比如, 要发布到 "
"Apache Tomcat, 你可以配置 <literal>tomcat-maven-plugin</literal>, 然后执行 "
"Maven 目标(goal) <literal>tomcat:deploy</literal>. 详情请参照插件本身的文档. "
"如果对某种特定的服务器类型, 没有可用的 Maven 插件, 你也可以通过某些低级别的方"
"法发布你的应用程序, 比如, 执行某个 Ant task."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the following, we create a run/debug configuration to build, deploy, and "
"launch a Vaadin Maven application on the light-weight Jetty web server."
msgstr ""
"下面我们介绍如何创建一个 run/debug 配置项, 来构建一个 Vaadin Maven 应用程序, "
"并在轻量级Jetty Web 服务器上发布和运行它."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Configurations</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>Run</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Configurations</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>+</guimenu><guimenuitem>Maven</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to create a new Maven run/debug configuration."
msgstr ""
"选择 <menuchoice><guimenu>+</guimenu><guimenuitem>Maven</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, 创建新的 Maven run/debug 配置项."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a <guilabel>Name</guilabel> for the run configuration. For the "
"<guilabel>Command line</guilabel>, enter \"<literal>package jetty:run</"
"literal> to first compile and package the project, and then launch Jetty to "
"run it."
msgstr ""
"为 run 配置项输入 <guilabel>Name</guilabel>. 对于 <guilabel>Command line</"
"guilabel>, 输入 \"<literal>package jetty:run</literal>, 这个命令首先将编译并"
"打包工程, 然后将启动 Jetty 来运行这个工程."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the run configuration in the toolbar and click the <guibutton>Run</"
"guibutton> button beside it."
msgstr ""
"在工具条中选择 run 设定项, 并点击它旁边的 <guibutton>Run</guibutton> 按钮."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compiling the project takes some time on the first time, as it compiles the "
"widget set and theme. Once the run console pane informs that Jetty Server "
"has been started, you can open the browser at the default URL <uri>http://"
"localhost:8080/</uri>."
msgstr ""
"初次编译工程时将耗费一些时间, 因为需要编译 widget 群和 theme. 当运行结果的控"
"制台输出面板中提示 Jetty 服务器启动完毕, 你就可以打开浏览器访问默认的URL: "
"<uri>http://localhost:8080/</uri>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vaadin Installation Package"
msgstr "Vaadin 安装包"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While the recommended way to install Vaadin is to use the Eclipse plugin, "
"one of the other IDE plugins, or a dependency management system, such as "
"Maven, Vaadin is also available as a ZIP distribution package."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐的 Vaadin 安装方式是使用 Eclipse 插件, 或者使用其他 IDE 的插件, 或者"
"使用包依赖管理系统, 比如 Maven, 但 Vaadin 也可以通过 ZIP 包的形式安装."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can download the newest Vaadin installation package from the download "
"page at <link xlink:href=\"http://vaadin.com/download/\">http://vaadin.com/"
"download/</link>. Please use a ZIP decompression utility available in your "
"operating system to extract the files from the ZIP package."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过下载页面得到最新的 Vaadin 安装包, 地址是 <link xlink:href=\"http://"
"vaadin.com/download/\">http://vaadin.com/download/</link>. 请用你操作系统中"
"的 ZIP 解压缩工具将 ZIP 包中的文件解开."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Package Contents"
msgstr "包中的内容"

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid "README.TXT"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This Readme file gives simple instructions for installing Vaadin in your "
"project."
msgstr "这是 Readme 文件, 简单介绍如何将 Vaadin 安装到你的工程中."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2291
#, no-c-format
msgid "release-notes.html"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Release Notes contain information about the new features in the "
"particular release, give upgrade instructions, describe compatibility, etc. "
"Please open the HTML file with a web browser."
msgstr ""
"发布说明文件, 其中的信息包括: 这个发布版的新功能特性, 升级方法指南, 与旧版本"
"之间的兼容问题, 等等等等. 这个 HTML 请通过浏览器阅读."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid "license.html"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apache License version 2.0. Please open the HTML file with a web browser."
msgstr "Apache License version 2.0. 这个 HTML 请通过浏览器阅读."

#. Tag: term
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2310
#, no-c-format
msgid "<filename>lib</filename> folder"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All dependency libraries required by Vaadin are contained within the "
"<filename>lib</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"Vaadin 所依赖的全部库文件都包含在这个 <filename>lib</filename> 文件夹中."

#. Tag: filename
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid "*.jar"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vaadin libraries, as described in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.libraries"
"\"/>."
msgstr "Vaadin 库, 详情参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-started.libraries\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing the Libraries"
msgstr "安装库文件"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2332
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can install the Vaadin ZIP package in a few simple steps:"
msgstr "你可以通过以下几个简单的步骤来安装 Vaadin ZIP 包:"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the JAR files at the package root folder to the <filename>WEB-APP/lib</"
"filename> web library folder in the project. Some of the libraries are "
"optional, as explained in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.libraries\"/>."
msgstr ""
"将包内根路径下的 JAR 文件复制到工程的 Web 库文件夹 <filename>WEB-APP/lib</"
"filename> 之下. 库文件中有一部分是可选的, 详情参见 <xref linkend=\"getting-"
"started.libraries\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also copy the dependency JAR files at the <filename>lib</filename> folder to "
"the <filename>WEB-APP/lib</filename> web library folder in the project."
msgstr ""
"将 <filename>lib</filename> 文件下的依赖 JAR 文件也复制到工程的 Web 库文件夹 "
"<filename>WEB-APP/lib</filename> 之下."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the <filename>WEB-APP/lib</filename> folder depends on the "
"project organization, which depends on the development environment."
msgstr ""
"在不同的开发环境中, 工程的组织结构会不同, 因此 <filename>WEB-APP/lib</"
"filename> 文件夹的位置也会不同."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Eclipse Dynamic Web Application projects: <filename>WebContent/WEB-INF/"
"lib</filename>."
msgstr ""
"在 Eclipse Dynamic Web Application 工程中, 它的路径是: <filename>WebContent/"
"WEB-INF/lib</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2366
#, no-c-format
msgid "In Maven projects: <filename>src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/lib</filename>."
msgstr ""
"在 Maven 工程中, 它的路径是: <filename>src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/lib</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Vaadin with Scala"
msgstr "在 Scala 中使用 Vaadin"

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use Vaadin with any JVM compatible language, such as Scala or "
"Groovy. There are, however, some caveats related to libraries and project "
"set-up. In the following, we give instructions for creating a Scala UI in "
"Eclipse, with the Scala IDE for Eclipse and the Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse."
msgstr ""
"在任何 JVM 兼容的语言中都可以使用 Vaadin, 比如 Scala 或 Groovy. 但是, 也存在"
"一些与库文件及工程设定相关的注意事项. 本节将介绍在 Eclipse 中如何用 Scala 创"
"建UI, 用到的工具是 Scala IDE for Eclipse 和 Vaadin Plugin for Eclipse."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Install the <link xlink:href=\"http://scala-ide.org/\">Scala IDE for "
"Eclipse</link>, either from an Eclipse update site or as a bundled Eclipse "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"安装 <link xlink:href=\"http://scala-ide.org/\">Scala IDE for Eclipse</"
"link>, 可以使用 Eclipse 更新站点, 也可以使用打包好的 Eclipse 发布包."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open an existing Vaadin Java project or create a new one as outlined in "
"<xref linkend=\"getting-started.first-project\"/>. You can delete the UI "
"class created by the wizard."
msgstr ""
"打开一个已有的 Vaadin Java 工程, 或者也可以创建一个新的工程, 方法参见 <xref "
"linkend=\"getting-started.first-project\"/>. 你可以删除向导自动创建的 UI 类."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to the Scala perspective by clicking the perspective in the upper-"
"right corner of the Eclipse window."
msgstr ""
"在 Eclipse 窗口右上侧点击 perspective , 切换到 Scala 透视图(perspective)."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the project folder in <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> "
"and select <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Scala "
"Nature</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"在 <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> 中, 在 project 上点击鼠标右键, 选择"
"菜单项 <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Scala "
"Nature</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The web application needs <filename>scala-library.jar</filename> in its "
"class path. If using Scala IDE, you can copy it from somewhere under your "
"Eclipse installation to the class path of the web application, that is, "
"either to the <filename>WebContent/WEB-INF/lib</filename> folder in the "
"project or to the library path of the application server. If copying outside "
"Eclipse to a project, refresh the project by selecting it and pressing "
"<keycap>F5</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Web 应用程序将需要 <filename>scala-library.jar</filename> 添加到它的类路径"
"中. 如果使用 Scala IDE, 你可以将这个 JAR 文件从你的 Eclipse 安装路径下的某个"
"地方复制到 Web 应用程序的类路径中, Web 应用程序的类路径可以是工程下的 "
"<filename>WebContent/WEB-INF/lib</filename> 文件夹, 或者是应用程序服务器的库"
"文件路径. 如果 JAR 文件的复制操作是在 Eclipse 外部进行的, 你需要刷新工程信息"
"才能在 Eclipse 内看到复制后的文件, 方法是选中工程, 然后按下快捷键 "
"<keycap>F5</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could also get it with an Ivy or Maven dependency, just make sure that "
"the version is same as what the Scala IDE uses."
msgstr ""
"你也可以在 Ivy 或 Maven 中添加对 Scala 的依赖来得到 Scala 运行库, 但主要要将"
"你依赖的 Scala 版本设置为 Scala IDE 使用的 Scala 版本一致."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should now be able to create a Scala UI class, such as the following:"
msgstr "现在可以用 Scala 创建 UI 类了, 方法如下:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<?pocket-size 75% ?><![CDATA[@Theme(\"mytheme\")\n"
"class MyScalaUI extends UI {\n"
"  override def init(request: VaadinRequest) = {\n"
"    val content: VerticalLayout = new VerticalLayout\n"
"    setContent(content)\n"
"\n"
"    val label: Label = new Label(\"Hello, world!\")\n"
"    content addComponent label\n"
"\n"
"    // Handle user interaction\n"
"    content addComponent new Button(\"Click Me!\",\n"
"      new ClickListener {\n"
"        override def buttonClick(event: ClickEvent) =\n"
"          Notification.show(\"The time is \" + new Date)\n"
"      })\n"
"  }\n"
"}]]>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eclipse and Scala IDE should be able to import the Vaadin classes "
"automatically when you press <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Shift</"
"keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"当你按下快捷键 <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Shift</"
"keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>, Eclipse 和 Scala IDE 将会自动导入 "
"Vaadin 类."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to define the Scala UI class either in a servlet class (in Servlet "
"3.0 project) or in a <filename>web.xml</filename> deployment descriptor, "
"just like described in <xref linkend=\"getting-started.first-project."
"exploring\"/> for Java UIs."
msgstr ""
"你需要将 Scala 语言的 UI 类定义在 Servlet 类中(对于 Servlet 3.0 工程), 或者定"
"义在 <filename>web.xml</filename> 部署描述文件中, 方法与 <xref linkend="
"\"getting-started.first-project.exploring\"/> 中介绍的 Java 语言 UI 类一样."

#. Tag: para
#: chapter-getting-started.xml:2454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link xlink:href=\"https://github.com/henrikerola/scaladin\">Scaladin "
"add-on</link> enables a more Scala-like API for Vaadin. A Vaadin 7 "
"compatible version is under development."
msgstr ""
"插件 <link xlink:href=\"https://github.com/henrikerola/scaladin\">Scaladin "
"add-on</link> 提供了一种更加符合 Scala 语言风格的 Vaadin API. 这个插件与 "
"Vaadin 7 兼容的版本目前还在开发中."
